msgstr "上下文相关模式"

#. :src: bpy.types.CloudRig_RigPreferences.context_sensitive
msgid "Hide rig properties with no relevant bones selected."
msgstr "未选中相关骨骼时隐藏骨架属性"

#. :src: bpy.types.CloudRig_RigPreferences.hide_during_transform
msgid "Hide UI During Transformations"
msgstr "变换期间隐藏界面"

#. :src: bpy.types.CloudRig_RigPreferences.hide_during_transform
msgid "Drawing this UI can be expensive depending on rig complexity. This option can alleviate that by disabling drawing during transformations. However, this can cause the scrollbar to reset to the top due to transformations."
msgstr "根据骨架复杂度,绘制此界面可能会很耗性能.此选项可以通过在变换期间禁用它来缓解这一问题.但是,这可能会导致滚动条因变换而重置到顶部."

#. :src: bpy.types.CloudRig_RigPreferences.show_bone_count
msgid "Bone Count"
msgstr "骨骼计数"

#. :src: bpy.types.CloudRig_RigPreferences.show_bone_count
msgid "Show number of bones selected/assigned (including child collections)"
msgstr "显示选中/分配的骨骼数量(包括子集合)"

#. :src: bpy.types.CloudRig_RigPreferences.show_editing
msgid "Show collection editing functions"
msgstr "显示集合编辑功能"

#. :src: bpy.types.CloudRig_RigPreferences.show_local_overrides
msgid "Show Link"
msgstr "显示链接"

#. :src: bpy.types.CloudRig_RigPreferences.show_local_overrides
msgid "Show an icon indicating whether a collection is a local override. Locally created collections can be renamed, removed, sorted, and parented amongst each other, but the linked collection tree from the original file cannot be modified"
msgstr "显示一个图标,指示集合是否为本地覆盖.本地创建的集合可以重命名移除,排序和相互设置父级,但无法修改来自原始文件的链接集合树"

#. :src: bpy.types.CloudRig_RigPreferences.show_select
msgid "Show the Select operator"
msgstr "显示选择操作符"

#. :src: bpy.types.CloudRig_RigPreferences.show_solo
msgid "Show the Solo operator"
msgstr "单独显示操作"

#. :src: bpy.types.CloudRig_RigPreferences.show_visibility
msgid "Show the Hide setting"
msgstr "显示隐藏设置"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties
msgid "RNA data used by the CloudRig Generator."
msgstr "CloudRig Generator 使用的 RNA 数据。"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.auto_setup_gizmos
msgid "Auto Setup Gizmos (EXPERIMENTAL)"
msgstr "自动设置Gizmo(实验性)"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.auto_setup_gizmos
msgid "Experiment with the initial BoneGizmo addon integration"
msgstr "试用初始BoneGizmo插件集成"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.base_wire_width
msgid "Base Wire Width"
msgstr "基础线框宽度"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.base_wire_width
msgid "Additional wire width to apply to all generated bones"
msgstr "要应用于所有生成骨骼的额外线框宽度"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.custom_script
msgid "Post-Generation Script"
msgstr "生成后执行脚本"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.custom_script
msgid "Execute a python script after the rig is generated"
msgstr "生成骨架后执行Python脚本"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.ensure_root
msgid "Root Bone"
msgstr "根骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.ensure_root
msgid "Bones that would otherwise be orphaned will be parented to this bone. This bone is also considered the root for FK Hinge set-ups. If the this root bone doesn't exist, it will be created, also in the metarig. This root bone does not have to be the true root: It is allowed to have parents!"
msgstr "孤立骨骼将自动父级化到此骨骼.此骨骼也用作 FK 铰链设置的根.若该根骨骼不存在,则会在元骨架中一并创建.此根骨骼不必是真正的根:允许它有父级!"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.generate_test_action
msgid "Generate Test Action"
msgstr "生成测试动作"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.generate_test_action
msgid "Whether to create/update the deform test action or not. Enabling this enables the Animation parameter category on FK chain components"
msgstr "是否创建/更新变形测试动作.启用此选项将在FK链组件上启用\"动画\"参数类别"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.preserve_custom_shapes
msgid "Preserve Custom Shapes"
msgstr "保留自定义形状"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.preserve_custom_shapes
msgid "Preserve custom shapes on the Target Rig, if available. If this is disabled, only other properties will be preserved, but not the shape object"
msgstr "如果可用,保留目标骨架上的自定义形状.如果禁用,则仅保留其他属性,但不保留形状对象"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.preserve_shapes_properties
msgid "Preserve Shape Properties"
msgstr "保留形状属性"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.preserve_shapes_properties
msgid "Preserve custom shape properties on the Target Rig, if available"
msgstr "如果可用,保留目标骨架上的自定义形状属性"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.properties_bone
#. :src: bpy.types.Params.props_storage_bone
msgid "Properties Bone"
msgstr "属性骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.properties_bone
msgid "Bone to use as the default custom property storage. Can be the same as the root bone. If it doesn't exist and is required, a bone named 'Properties' will be created on the metarig"
msgstr "用作默认自定义属性存储的骨骼.可以与根骨骼相同.如果不存在且需要,将在元骨架上创建一个名为\"属性\"的骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.reload_widgets
msgid "Overwrite Custom Shapes"
msgstr "覆盖自定义形状"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.reload_widgets
msgid "Reload custom shapes, discarding any local modifications to them"
msgstr "重新加载自定义形状,放弃对其的任何本地修改"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.target_rig
msgid "Target Rig"
msgstr "目标骨架"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.target_rig
msgid "Rig to re-genreate based on this metarig when the Generate button is used"
msgstr "使用生成按钮时基于此元骨架重新生成的骨架"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.test_action
msgid "Test Action"
msgstr "测试动作"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.test_action
msgid "Action which will be generated with the keyframes neccessary to test the rig's deformations"
msgstr "将生成的动作,包含测试骨架变形所需的关键帧"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.widget_collection
msgid "Custom Shape Collection"
msgstr "自定义形状集合"

#. :src: bpy.types.GeneratorProperties.widget_collection
msgid "Collection dedicated to storing nothing but the custom shapes used by this rig. Additional objects will result in warnings, and missing custom shapes will be re-linked during generation"
msgstr "专用于仅存储此骨架使用的自定义形状的集合.额外的对象将导致警告,缺失的自定义形状将在生成期间重新链接"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.create_deform
#. :src: bpy.types.Params.deform
msgid "Create Deform"
msgstr "创建形变"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.create_deform
msgid "Create a deforming child bone for this bone, prefixed with \"DEF-\""
msgstr "为此骨骼创建一个变形的子骨骼,前缀为\"DEF-\""

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.custom_pivot
msgid "Create Custom Pivot"
msgstr "创建自定义枢轴"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.custom_pivot
msgid "Create a parent control whose local translation is not propagated to the main control, but its rotation and scale are"
msgstr "创建一个父控制,其局部平移不会传播到主控制,但其旋转和缩放会传播"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.ensure_free
msgid "Ensure Free Transforms"
msgstr "确保自由变换"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.ensure_free
msgid "If this bone has any drivers on its transform properties or constraints, move them to a parent bone prefixed with \"CON\", except for constraints whose name starts with \"KEEP\""
msgstr "如果此骨骼在其变换属性或约束上有任何驱动器,则将它们移动到前缀为\"CON\"的父骨骼上,名称以\"KEEP\"开头的约束除外"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.property_ui_label
#: E:/Git/Extensions/CloudRig/rig_component_features/parenting.py:107
msgid "UI Label"
msgstr "界面标签"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.property_ui_label
msgid "Choose which label the custom properties should be displayed under. If empty, the properties will display at the top of the subpanel"
msgstr "选择自定义属性应显示在哪个标签下.如果为空,属性将显示在子面板顶部"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.property_ui_subpanel
msgid "UI Sub-panel"
msgstr "UI子面板"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.property_ui_subpanel
msgid "Choose which sub-panel the custom properties should be displayed in. If empty, the properties won't appear in the rig UI"
msgstr "选择自定义属性应显示在哪个子面板中.如果为空.属性将不会出现在骨架界面中"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.shrinkwrap_mesh
msgid "Shrinkwrap Mesh"
msgstr "收缩包裹网格"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.shrinkwrap_mesh
msgid "Mesh object to shrinkwrap to using Shrinkwrap Constraints."
msgstr "要使用收缩包裹约束收缩包裹到的网格对象"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.sphere_bone
msgid "Sphere Bone"
msgstr "球体骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.sphere_bone
msgid "Bone to use as the center of the sphere."
msgstr "用作球体中心的骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.align_roll
msgid "Align Roll"
msgstr "对齐滚动"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.align_roll
msgid "Re-calculate the bone roll of STR controls based on the ORG bones"
msgstr "基于ORG骨骼重新计算STR控制的骨骼滚动"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.bbone_density
msgid "B-Bone Density"
msgstr "B-骨骼密度"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.bbone_density
msgid "Average number of B-Bone Segments per deform bone. Longer bones will have more, shorter ones fewer, to get an even distribution. There will be a minimum of 2 B-Bone Segments unless this parameter is 0"
msgstr "每个变形骨骼的平均B骨骼段数.较长的骨骼将更多,较短的更少,以获得均匀分布.除非此参数为0,否则至少有2个B骨骼段"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.preserve_volume
msgid ""
"The bone will become thinner and thicker depending on stretching length.\n"
"\n"
"NOTE: This will result in non-uniform scale inheritance when scaling root bones!"
msgstr ""
"骨骼将根据拉伸长度变细或变粗.\n"
"\n"
"注意:缩放根骨骼时,这将导致不均匀的缩放继承!"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.segments
msgid "Stretch Segments"
msgstr "拉伸段"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.segments
msgid "Number of bendy bones to create for each original bone"
msgstr "为每个原始骨骼创建的弯曲骨骼数量"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.shape_key_helpers
msgid "Create Shape Key Helpers"
msgstr "创建形态键辅助"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.shape_key_helpers
msgid "Create SKH bones that read the rotation between two deform bones, which can be used to drive corrective shape keys"
msgstr "创建读取两个变形骨骼之间旋转的SKH骨骼,可用于驱动校正形态键"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.shape_size
msgid "Custom Shape Size"
msgstr "自定义形状大小"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.sharp
msgid "Sharp Sections"
msgstr "锐利段"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.sharp
msgid "B-Bone EaseIn/Out is set to 0 for bones connecting two sections"
msgstr "对于连接两个段的骨骼,B骨骼缓入/缓出设置为0"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.smooth_spline
msgid "Smooth Spline"
msgstr "平滑样条"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.smooth_spline
msgid "B-Bone Splines affect their neighbours for smoother curves"
msgstr "B骨骼样条影响其相邻骨骼以获得更平滑的曲线"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.tip_control
msgid "Tip Control"
msgstr "末端控制"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.tip_control
msgid "Add the final control at the end of the chain. Disabling this allows you to connect another chain to this one, or to make this chain loop into itself"
msgstr "在链末端添加最终控制.禁用此选项允许您将另一个链连接到该链,或使该链自身循环"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.unlock_deform
msgid "Create Deform Controls"
msgstr "创建变形控制"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.unlock_deform
msgid "Create CTR-DEF controls that allow Deform bones to be controlled directly"
msgstr "创建CTR-DEF控制,允许直接控制变形骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.volume_variation
msgid "How exaggerated the squashing and stretching should be"
msgstr "挤压和拉伸夸张程度"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.bbone_props
msgid "B-Bone Properties"
msgstr "B-骨骼属性"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.bbone_props
msgid "Copy B-Bone settings from this bone to the generated bone"
msgstr "将此骨骼的B骨骼设置复制到生成的骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.collections
msgid "Assign the matching generated bone to the collections of this tweak bone"
msgstr "将匹配的生成骨骼分配到此调整骨骼的集合"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.color_palette
msgid "Set the generated bone's colors to this bone's colors"
msgstr "将生成骨骼的颜色设置为此骨骼的颜色"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.constraints_additive
msgid "Additive Constraints"
msgstr "附加约束"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.constraints_additive
msgid "Add the constraints of this bone to the generated bone's constraints. When disabled, we replace the constraints instead"
msgstr "将此骨骼的约束添加到生成的骨骼的约束中.禁用时,我们将替换约束"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.custom_props
msgid "Copy custom properties from this bone to the generated bone"
msgstr "将此骨骼的自定义属性复制到生成的骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.ik_settings
msgid "IK Properties"
msgstr "IK 属性"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.ik_settings
msgid "Copy IK settings from this bone to the generated bone"
msgstr "将此骨骼的IK设置复制到生成的骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.locks
msgid "Locks"
msgstr "锁定"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.locks
msgid "Replace the matching generated bone's transform locks with this bone's transform locks"
msgstr "将此骨骼的变换锁定替换匹配的生成骨骼的变换锁定"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.rot_mode
msgid "Set the matching generated bone's rotation mode to this bone's rotation mode"
msgstr "将匹配的生成骨骼的旋转模式设置为此骨骼的旋转模式"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.shape
msgid "Bone Shape"
msgstr "骨骼形状"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.shape
msgid "Replace the matching generated bone's shape with this bone's shape"
msgstr "将此骨骼的形状替换匹配的生成骨骼的形状"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.transforms
msgid "Replace the matching generated bone's transforms with this bone's transforms"
msgstr "将此骨骼的变换替换匹配的生成骨骼的变换"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.bbone_segments
msgid "Bendy Segments"
msgstr "弯曲段"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.bbone_segments
msgid "While the bendy bone curvature doesn't take the curve's curvature into account, it can still help smoothen the deformation"
msgstr "虽然弯曲骨骼的曲率不考虑曲线的曲率,但它仍然有助于平滑变形"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.create_fk_chain
msgid "Create FK Chain"
msgstr "创建FK链"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.create_fk_chain
msgid "Create an FK chain on top of the hook controls"
msgstr "在钩子控制之上创建FK链"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.deform_setup
msgid "Deform Setup"
msgstr "形变设置"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.deform_setup
msgid "How this curve rig component should behave with Armature modifiers"
msgstr "此曲线骨架组件应如何与骨架修改器交互"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.deform_setup:'NONE'
msgid "Disable deform flag, so this component won't work with Armature modifiers"
msgstr "禁用变形标志,因此此组件将不与骨架修改器配合工作"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.deform_setup:'PRESERVE'
msgid "Preserve deform flag of each bone"
msgstr "保留每个骨骼的变形标志"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.deform_setup:'CREATE'
msgid "Create"
msgstr "创建"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.deform_setup:'CREATE'
msgid "Create deform bones prefixed with DEF-"
msgstr "创建以DEF-为前缀的变形骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.handle_length
msgid "Curve Handle Length"
msgstr "曲线手柄长度"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.handle_length
msgid "Increasing this will result in longer curve handles, resulting in a sharper curve. A value of 1 means the curve handle reaches the neighbouring curve point"
msgstr "增加此值将产生更长的曲线手柄,从而产生更尖锐的曲线.值为1表示曲线手柄到达相邻曲线点"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.hooks
#. :src: bpy.types.Params.num_hooks
msgid "Number of Hooks"
msgstr "挂钩数量"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.hooks
msgid "Number of controls that will be spaced out evenly across the entire chain"
msgstr "将在整个链上均匀分布的控制数量"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.match_hooks
msgid "Match Controls to Bones"
msgstr "匹配控制与骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.match_hooks
msgid "Hook controls will be created at each bone, instead of being equally distributed across the length of the chain"
msgstr "挂钩控制将在每个骨骼处创建,而不是在链的长度上均匀分布"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.subdivide
msgid "Subdivide Bones"
msgstr "细分骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.subdivide
msgid "For each original bone, create this many deform bones in the spline chain (Bendy Bones don't take the curve into account, so it's best to use quite a few real bones) NOTE: Spline IK only supports 255 bones in the chain"
msgstr "对于每个原始骨骼,在样条链中创建这么多变形骨骼(弯曲骨骼不考虑曲线,因此最好使用相当多的真实骨骼)注意:样条IK仅支持链中最多255个骨"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params
msgid "Defines the parameters to be registered in RNA. Must be exactly `Params`."
msgstr "定义要在RNA中注册的参数.必须恰好是`Params`."

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.default_fkik
msgid "Default FK/IK"
msgstr "默认FK/IK"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.default_stretch
msgid "Default IK Squash"
msgstr "默认 IK 挤压"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.flatten_controls
msgid "Flatten Controls (Deprecated)"
msgstr "扁平化控件(已弃用)"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.flatten_controls
msgid "Align torso and hip controls with the closest world axis. This option is deprecated and will be removed in Blender 6.0 in favor of 'World Align Controls'."
msgstr "将躯干和臀部控制与最近的世界坐标轴对齐。此选项已弃用，将在 Blender 6.0 中移除，取而代之的是“世界坐标轴对齐控制”"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.world_align
msgid "World-Align Torso"
msgstr "世界坐标对齐躯干"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.world_align
msgid "Align the torso control with the world axes"
msgstr "将躯干控制与世界坐标轴对齐"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.double
msgid "Duplicate Controls"
msgstr "复制控制"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.double
msgid "Make duplicates of the main spine controls"
msgstr "复制主脊椎控制"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.world_align
msgid "World-Align Controls"
msgstr "世界坐标对齐"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.world_align
msgid "Flatten the torso and hips to align with the closest world axis"
msgstr "展平躯干和臀部以对齐最近的世界轴"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.use_ik
msgid "Create IK Spine"
msgstr "创建IK脊椎"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.use_ik
msgid "If disabled, this spine rig will only have FK controls"
msgstr "如果禁用,此脊椎骨架将只有FK控制"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.world_align
msgid "Align the torso and hip controls with the world axes"
msgstr "将躯干和臀部控制与世界坐标轴对"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.parent_switching
#: E:/Git/Extensions/CloudRig/rig_components/cloud_fk_chain.py:64
#: E:/Git/Extensions/CloudRig/rig_components/cloud_ik_chain.py:71
#: E:/Git/Extensions/CloudRig/rig_components/cloud_limb.py:61
msgid "Parent Switching"
msgstr "父级切换"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.parent_switching
msgid "Use parent switching for this rig. Different rig types may implement this differently. A rig-type-specific explanation is shown below when enabled"
msgstr "为此骨架使用父级切换.不同的骨架类型可能以不同方式实现.启用时,下方将显示特定于骨架类型的说明"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.root_parent
#: E:/Git/Extensions/CloudRig/rig_component_features/parenting.py:366
msgid "Root Parent"
msgstr "根父级"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.root_parent
msgid "If specified, parent the root of this rig to the chosen bone. If a bendy bone is chosen, a parent helper bone with an Armature Constraint will be created to correctly inherit transforms from the curvature"
msgstr "如果指定,则将此骨架的根父级到所选骨骼.如果选择了弯曲骨骼,将创建一个带有骨架约束的父辅助骨骼,以正确地从曲率继承变换"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.use_armature_constraint
msgid "Use Armature Constraint"
msgstr "使用骨架约束"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.use_armature_constraint
msgid "Instead of directly parenting this bone to the parent, use an Armature constraint. This allows the bone to follow the parent's bendy bone curvature"
msgstr "不直接将此骨骼父级到父级,而是使用骨架约束.这允许骨骼跟随父级的弯曲骨骼曲率"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.use_helper_bone
msgid "Create Parent Helper"
msgstr "创建父级辅助骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.use_helper_bone
msgid "Instead of adding the Armature constraint directly to this bone, create a parent bone prefixed with 'P-' and add it to that one instead. This will keep the local transformations of this bone clear from any parenting-induced transformations, as would be the case with normal parenting"
msgstr "不直接将骨架约束添加到此骨骼,而是创建一个前缀为\"P-\"的父骨骼,并将约束添加到该骨骼.这将使此骨骼的局部变换不受任何父级引起的变换的影响,而常规父级则会受到影响"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.handle_length
msgid "Auto-generated curve's bezier handle length, as a fraction of the distance between hooks"
msgstr ""

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.num_hooks
msgid "Number of hook points to create when auto-generating a curve (only used if no curve is assigned)"
msgstr ""

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.use_pole
msgid "Create IK Pole"
msgstr "创建IK极"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.use_pole
msgid "If enabled, create an IK pole target for each spline to control the bend direction of the IK chain"
msgstr ""

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.props_storage
msgid "Custom Property Storage"
msgstr "自定义属性存储"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.props_storage
msgid "Where to store the custom properties needed for this rig component"
msgstr "存储此骨架组件所需的自定义属性的位置"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.props_storage:'DEFAULT'
msgid "Shared"
msgstr "共用骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.props_storage:'DEFAULT'
msgid "Use a shared bone called \"Properties\""
msgstr "使用名为\"属性\"的共享骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.props_storage:'CUSTOM'
msgid "Picked"
msgstr "已选择"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.props_storage:'CUSTOM'
msgid "Select an existing bone"
msgstr "选择现有骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.props_storage:'GENERATED'
msgid "Generate a bone specifically for this rig component, prefixed \"PRP-\""
msgstr "专门为此骨架组件生成一个骨骼,前缀为\"PRP-\""

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.props_storage_bone
msgid "Store custom properties in the chosen bone. If empty, will fall back to a bone called \"Properties\""
msgstr "将自定义属性存储在所选骨骼中.如果为空,将回退到名为\"属性\"的骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.up_axis
msgid "Custom Shape Up Axis"
msgstr "自定义形状朝上轴"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.up_axis
msgid "Rotate the bone shape to align with this axis of the bone"
msgstr "旋转骨骼形状以与该骨骼的此轴对齐"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.up_axis:'0'
msgid "Do not rotate the bone shape"
msgstr "不旋转骨骼形状"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.up_axis:'1'
msgid "Rotate bone shape by 90 degrees"
msgstr "将骨骼形状旋转90度"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.up_axis:'2'
msgid "Rotate bone shape by 180 degrees"
msgstr "将骨骼形状旋转180度"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.up_axis:'3'
msgid "Rotate bone shape by -90 degrees"
msgstr "将骨骼形状旋转-90度"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.force_regen
msgid "Force Re-generate"
msgstr "强制重新生成"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.force_regen
msgid "Even if the mesh already exists, force it to be re-generated from scratch"
msgstr "即使网格已存在,也强制从头开始重新生成"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.make_ctrl
msgid "Create Physics Controls"
msgstr "创建物理控制"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.make_ctrl
msgid "Create a control chain that can control the physics mesh using an Armature modifier"
msgstr "创建一个控制链,可以使用骨架修改器控制物理网格"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.phys_obj
msgid "Cloth Object"
msgstr "布料对象"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.phys_obj
msgid "Select an object which has vertex groups corresponding to the bone names of the chain, prefixed with 'phys_'. Leave empty to generate the object"
msgstr "选择一个对象,该对象具有与链的骨骼名称对应的顶点组,前缀为\"phys_\".留空以生成对象"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.pin_falloff
msgid "Pin Falloff"
msgstr "固定衰减"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.pin_falloff
msgid "Type of falloff to apply to the generated cloth mesh's pin vertex group. The first vertex is always fully pinned"
msgstr "应用于生成的布料网格的固定顶点组的衰减类型.第一个顶点始终完全固定"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.pin_falloff:'NONE'
msgid "First vertex fully pinned, rest fully unpinned"
msgstr "第一个顶点完全固定,其余完全未固定"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.pin_falloff:'LINEAR'
msgid "First vertex fully pinned, last vertex not pinned at all, vertices inbetween are linear interpolated"
msgstr "第一个顶点完全固定,最后一个顶点完全不固定,中间顶点线性插值"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.pin_falloff:'QUADRATIC'
msgid "First vertex fully pinned, last vertex not pinned at all, vertices inbetween are linear interpolated and then raised to 2nd power"
msgstr "第一个顶点完全固定,最后一个顶点完全不固定,中间顶点线性插值后取平方"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.pin_falloff:'SQRT'
msgid "Stiff"
msgstr "刚性"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.pin_falloff:'SQRT'
msgid "First vertex fully pinned, last vertex not pinned at all, vertices inbetween are linear interpolated and then their square root is taken"
msgstr "第一个顶点完全固定,最后一个顶点完全不固定,中间顶点线性插值后取平方根"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.pin_falloff_offset
msgid "Pin Falloff Offset"
msgstr "固定衰减偏移"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.pin_falloff_offset
msgid "Calculate the pin falloffs as if the bone chain was this much longer than it actually is. Increasing this beyond 1.0 will cause all vertices to be more pinned"
msgstr "计算固定衰减时,仿佛骨骼链比实际长度长这么多.将其增加到1.0以上将导致所有顶点更加固定"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.auto_hose
msgid "Rubber Hose"
msgstr "软管"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.auto_hose
msgid "Add an Auto Rubber Hose setting which can be enabled to automatically add curvature to limbs as they bend. Stretch Segments parameter must be >1 and Smooth Spline must be enabled"
msgstr "添加一个自动软管设置,启用后可以在四肢弯曲时自动添加曲率.拉伸段参数必须大于1,且必须启用平滑样条"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.auto_hose_control
msgid "With Control"
msgstr "提供控制骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.auto_hose_control
msgid "Instead of controlling the Auto Rubber Hose property from the rig UI, create a control bone on the FK Extras layer"
msgstr "不在骨架界面中控制自动软管属性,而是在FK额外层上创建一个控制骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.auto_hose_type
msgid "The rubber hosing effect can be achieved in different ways. This lets you pick which one you prefer"
msgstr "软管效果可以通过不同方式实现.这可以让您选择您更喜欢的方式"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.auto_hose_type:'MIDDLE_OUT'
msgid "Long"
msgstr "长"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.auto_hose_type:'MIDDLE_OUT'
msgid "Shift mid-limb STR bones away from the elbow bending direction. As a result, the limb becomes longer"
msgstr "将肢体中部的STR骨骼移离肘部弯曲方向.结果,肢体变长"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.auto_hose_type:'ELBOW_IN'
msgid "Short"
msgstr "短"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.auto_hose_type:'ELBOW_IN'
msgid "Shift the elbow STR bone towards the elbow bending direction, and counter-shift the mid-limb STR bones so they stay roughly in place. As a result, the limb becomes shorter"
msgstr "肘部STR骨骼移向肘部弯曲方向,并将肢体中部的STR骨骼反向移动,使其大致保持在原位.结果,肢体变短"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.double_ik
msgid "Duplicate IK Master"
msgstr "复制IK主控制"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.double_ik
msgid "The IK control has a parent control. Having two controls for the same thing can help avoid interpolation issues when the common pose in animation is far from the rest pose"
msgstr "IK控制有一个父控制,对同一事物拥有两个控制有助于避免当动画中的常见姿势远离静止姿势时出现插值问题"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.limit_elbow_axes
msgid "Limit Elbow Axes"
msgstr "限制肘部轴"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.limit_elbow_axes
msgid "Lock the Y and Z rotation of the elbow/knee bone, only allowing realistic rotations. This is limiting for cartoony characters, but it's necessary for accurate FK->IK snapping. For realistic characters, this should be enabled. This also requires that the elbow bends along its local X axis"
msgstr "锁定肘/膝骨骼的Y和Z旋转,仅允许真实旋转.这对卡通角色有限制,但对于精确的FK到IK吸附是必要的.对于真实角色,应启用此选项.这还要求肘部沿其局部X轴弯曲"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.create_forefoot
msgid "Forefoot Control"
msgstr "前脚掌控制"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.create_forefoot
msgid "Create a control at the ball of the foot to pivot from."
msgstr "在脚掌处创建一个控制点，以此作为旋转轴。"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.heel_bone
msgid "Heel Pivot Bone"
msgstr "脚跟枢轴骨骼"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.heel_bone
msgid "(Optional.) Bone to use as the heel pivot. This bone should be placed at the heel of the shoe, pointing from the center outward, with its length defining the width of the shoe."
msgstr "(可选)用作脚跟枢轴的骨骼.此骨骼应放置在鞋跟处,从中心向外指向,其长度定义鞋的宽度"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.use_foot_roll
msgid "Foot Roll"
msgstr "脚部滚动"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.use_foot_roll
msgid "Create a Foot Roll control. When rotated 90 degrees on the X axis, the foot will be fully vertical (ie. on tippy-toes). Rotate it an additional 45 degrees, and the toe will also be vertical (like a ballerina). The angles are calculated based on the rest pose"
msgstr "创建一个脚部滚动控制.当在X轴上旋转90度时,脚将完全垂直(即踮脚).再旋转45度,脚趾也将垂直(如芭蕾舞者).角度基于静止姿势计算"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.lattice
msgid "Lattice Object that will be hooked up to this control. If not left empty, the already existing lattice will not be affected in any way, unless Regenerate Lattice is enabled"
msgstr "将连接到该控制的晶格对象.如果不留空,现有晶格将不受任何影响,除非启用重新生成晶格"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.regenerate
msgid "Regenerate"
msgstr "重新生成"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.regenerate
msgid "Whether to re-generate the lattice object on rig generation. Disable if you intend to modify the generated lattice object manually"
msgstr "是否在生成骨架时重新生成晶格对象.如果打算手动修改生成的晶格对象,请禁用"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.counter_rotate_stretch_bones
msgid "Counter-Rotate Stretch Controls"
msgstr "反向旋转拉伸控制"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.counter_rotate_stretch_bones
msgid "Rotating FK bones will counter-rotate the child stretch bones. This can result in smoother chains"
msgstr "旋转FK骨骼将使子拉伸骨骼反向旋转.这可以使链更平滑"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.create_curl_control
msgid "Curl Control"
msgstr "卷曲控制"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.create_curl_control
msgid "Create a control that lets you easily curl this FK chain. Can be useful for tails and fingers and such. Requires a root bone for space calculations"
msgstr "创建一个控制,让您可以轻松地卷曲此FK链.可用于尾巴、手指等.需要根骨骼进行空间计算"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.curl_each
msgid "Curl Each"
msgstr "逐节卷曲"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.curl_each
msgid "Each FK Control inherits local rotation from its parent, resulting in curling. This can be combined with the Curl Control, but it's not recommended."
msgstr "每个 FK 控制都会继承其父级的局部旋转,从而产生卷曲效果.虽然可以与卷曲控制结合使用,但不建议这样做."

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.display_center
msgid "Display Centered"
msgstr "居中显示"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.display_center
msgid "Display all FK controls' shapes in the center of the bone, rather than the beginning of the bone"
msgstr "将所有FK控制的形状显示在骨骼中心,而不是骨骼起点"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.double_first
msgid "Duplicate First FK"
msgstr "复制第一个FK"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.double_first
msgid "Create a parent control for the first FK control. This can be useful when the Rest Pose is far from the character's common pose, to avoid gimbal locking"
msgstr "为第一个FK控制创建一个父控制.当静止姿势远离角色的常见姿势时,这可能有助于避免万向锁"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.hinge
msgid "Set up a hinge toggle which allows this FK chain to not inherit rotation from its parent, but still inherit rotation from the rig root. There must be a root bone name specified in generator settings for this"
msgstr "设置一个铰链切换,允许此FK链不从其父级继承旋转,但仍从骨架根继承旋转.生成器设置中必须指定根骨骼名称"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.inherit_scale
msgid "Scale inheritance type for FK controls"
msgstr "FK控制的缩放继承类型"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.inherit_scale:'PROPAGATE'
msgid "Propagate scale inheritance mode from each meta bone to its corresponding control"
msgstr "将每个元骨骼的缩放继承模式传播到其对应的控制"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.root
#. :src: bpy.types.Params.create_root
msgid "Create Root"
msgstr "创建根"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.root
msgid "Create a root control"
msgstr "创建根控制"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.rot_mode
msgid "Set the rotation mode of the FK controls"
msgstr "设置FK控制的旋转模式"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.rot_mode:'PROPAGATE'
msgid "Propagate rotation mode from each meta bone to its corresponding control"
msgstr "将每个元骨骼的旋转模式传播到其对应的控制"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.test_animation_axes
#: E:/Git/Extensions/CloudRig/rig_components/cloud_fk_chain.py:493
msgid "Rotation Axes"
msgstr "旋转轴"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.test_animation_axes
msgid "Rotation axes to test in the test animation"
msgstr "在测试动画中测试的旋转轴"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.test_animation_generate
msgid "Generate Test Animation"
msgstr "生成测试动画"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.test_animation_generate
msgid "Include this rig component in the test animation"
msgstr "在测试动画中包含此骨架组件"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.test_animation_rotation_range
msgid "Rotation Range"
msgstr "旋转范围"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.test_animation_rotation_range
msgid "Minimum and Maximum rotations for the test animation"
msgstr "测试动画的最小和最大旋转"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.merge
msgid "Merge Controls"
msgstr "合并控制"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.merge
msgid "If any controls of this rig intersect with another, create a parent control that owns all overlapping controls, and hide the overlapping controls on a different layer"
msgstr "如果此骨架的任何控制与另一个相交,则创建一个拥有所有重叠控制的父控制,并将重叠控制在另一层上隐藏"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.base_name
#: E:/Git/Extensions/CloudRig/rig_components/cloud_base.py:289
msgid "Base Name"
msgstr "基础名称"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.base_name
msgid "Optional. If provided, use this as the base name for some generated bones and properties, rather than the bone name. This should not include a side indicator (\"Left\"/\"Right\"), as that willbe added automatically"
msgstr "可选.如果提供,用作某些生成的骨骼和属性的基础名称,而不是骨骼名称.不应包含侧边指示(\"左\"/\"右\"),因为这些将自动添加"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.at_tip
msgid "IK At Tail"
msgstr "IK在末端"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.at_tip
msgid "Put the IK control at the tail of the chain, rather than the head of the last bone"
msgstr "将IK控制放在链的末端,而不是最后一根骨骼的头部"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.default_stretch
msgid "Default IK Stretch"
msgstr "默认IK拉伸"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.flatten_controls
msgid "Align the last controls with the closest world axis. This option is deprecated and will be removed in Blender 6.0 in favor of 'World Align Controls'."
msgstr "将最后一个控件与最近的世界坐标轴对齐。此选项已弃用，将在 Blender 6.0 中移除，取而代之的是“世界坐标轴对齐控件”"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.pole_parent_switch
msgid "Pole Parent Switching"
msgstr "极父级切换"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.pole_parent_switch
msgid "How the IK Pole's parent switching options should be determined."
msgstr "如何确定IK极的父级切换选项"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.pole_parent_switch:'FOLLOW'
msgid "The IK Pole is parented always to the same bone as the IK master, or to the IK master itself, determined by a single slider."
msgstr "IK极始终父级到与IK主控相同的骨骼,或父级到IK主控本身,由单个滑块决定"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.pole_parent_switch:'INDIVIDUAL'
msgid "The IK Pole gets the same parenting options as the IK Master, plus the IK Master itself as a parent option."
msgstr "IK极获得与IK主控相同的父级选项,加上IK主控本身作为父级选项"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.use_pole
msgid "If disabled, you can control the rotation of the IK chain by simply rotating its first bone, rather than with an IK pole control"
msgstr "如果禁用,您可以通过旋转其第一根骨骼来控制IK链的旋转,而不是使用IK极控制"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.world_align
msgid "Align the last controls with the world axes"
msgstr "将最后一个控件与世界坐标轴对齐"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.create_sub_control
msgid "Create Highlight"
msgstr "创建高光控制"

#. :src: bpy.types.Params.create_sub_control
